      <title>德州盟友警告称，特朗普的科技伙伴无法逃脱美国审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-s-tech-buddies-won-t-escape-us-scrutiny-texas-ally-warns</link>
