      <title>Meta 讨论在特拉华州以外地区重新开展业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/meta-discusses-reincorporating-its-business-outside-delaware</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Meta Platforms Inc. 正在讨论在特拉华州以外重新注册其业务，该公司自 2004 年成立以来一直在特拉华州合法注册。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/meta-discusses-reincorporating-its-business-outside-delaware</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 20:03:29 GMT</pubDate>
