    <item>
      <title>风险投资家沃尔夫呼吁加大投资力度，应对 DeepSeek“威胁”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/vc-wolfe-calls-for-more-investment-to-combat-deepseek-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lux Capital 联合创始人乔什·沃尔夫 (Josh Wolfe) 称中国人工智能初创公司 DeepSeek 是“严重的国家安全威胁”，并表示该公司以美国竞争对手成本的一小部分开发人工智能模型，对美国来说是一次重大“警钟”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/vc-wolfe-calls-for-more-investment-to-combat-deepseek-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 19:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia DeepSeek 股价下跌，华尔街关注关键股价点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nvidia-nvda-shares-hover-near-key-technical-level-after-deepseek-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街，所有人的目光都集中在英伟达公司的股票上，图表观察者寻找这家芯片制造巨头能否从 DeepSeek 引发的崩溃中恢复过来的迹象，因为其有能力左右更广泛的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nvidia-nvda-shares-hover-near-key-technical-level-after-deepseek-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 17:22:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
